<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.9">
<l>aṇṭattiṉ mukaṭaḻunta valaimunnīrt tiraitatumpa vāvāveṉṟu</l>
<l>toṇṭarkku mamararkkum muṉivarkkun tāṉaruḷi yulakamēḻum</l>
<l>uṇṭotta tiruvayiṟṟi ṉakampaṭiyil vaittummai yuyyakkoṇṭa</l>
<l>koṇṭaṟkai maṇivaṇṇaṉ taṇkuṭantai nakarppāṭi yāṭīrkaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Dance, singing of the cool city of Kuṭantai of the jewel-hued one,</l>
<l rend="indent">[his] hands [like bountiful] clouds,</l>
<l>Who, having consumed the seven worlds, granting grace</l>
<l rend="indent">to devotees, immortals, and sages, thinking, “Ah, [pity]!”</l>
<l>Took you, placing [you] into the depths of his divine, apt belly to save [you],</l>
<l>When the crashing waves of the three-watered [sea],</l>
<l rend="indent">which pressed against the roof of the firmament, flooded.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
